              <h4 className="text-xs font-black text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-tighter">Cinematic Logic</h4>
              <p className="text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
                Each shot in the 3x3 grid is specifically directed to tell a coherent story segment while strictly following the master lighting setup.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div className="space-y-3">
              <div className="w-8 h-8 bg-zinc-800 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-zinc-400">
                <Copy size={16} />
              </div>
              <h4 className="text-xs font-black text-zinc-300 uppercase tracking-tighter">One-Click Deploy</h4>
              <p className="text-[11px] text-zinc-500 leading-relaxed">
                Paste the generated prompt into Midjourney or Flux. The [3x3] instruction ensures the engine renders all viewpoints at once.
              </p>
